project_descr: The objective of the project is to transform Kazakhstan’s markets to energy efficient appliances and equipment, thereby reducing electricity consumption and GHG emissions

outputs.output_descr: The project will pursue regulations and labelling for the three categories of appliances and equipment with the highest electricity consumption and impact – refrigerators, industrial motors, and distribution transformers.

document_name: Ref.2018-0011_International Expert on Energy Efficiency in Production and Operation of Transformers in Kazakhstan
project_title: energy efficient standards, certification, and labelling
